Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.36,0:00:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，請保持房間光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在電視太近的地方收看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.08,0:00:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士的鋼鐵天使啟動了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個ANGEL HEART的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.68,0:00:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計劃成功了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.65,0:00:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若那個計劃真的成功了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人擔心的時代...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可以再坐視不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要立即展開調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒路可逃了，綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可能逃避軍隊的追捕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再繼續鋼鐵天使的研究吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓她成為殺人工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這個鋼鐵士兵，金剛一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你振作點唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，去破壞金剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹甚麼?快去破壞金剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.58,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是鋼鐵天使!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?這是我的命令，久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會聽從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不識的大叔的命令唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認識...的大叔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是大嬸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說，是我製造妳出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的親生父母啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是媽媽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，總而言之，快點逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦，救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人   主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在唯有用他做人質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，這個孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城，連妳也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會放過...欺負主人的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛不痛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...鋼鐵天使的力量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...我是不會退縮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的，金剛鐵拳的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以一次過摧毀十輛戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你真的不痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現...現在好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼我會遇到這種事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.31,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!救我啊!久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼我要救你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是製造妳出來的親生父母啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識你就是不認識你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如...   是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣也好，我們一起離開這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷，主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去哪裡?主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個朋友住在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡會安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去那兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士，妳沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別理我，博士他們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉，他們逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長，在瓦礫中發現了一個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?女孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士有甚麼頭緒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把我放下來再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我，嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神人，這位年輕人是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是舍弟，仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令弟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，博士為甚麼會來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人只是屬於久留美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動失敗了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會負責，我願意接受任何懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍，我們得到了研究對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,務必請將軍去參觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研究對象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是綾小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是神人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼妳叫仲人做主人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，久留美會以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一個啟動她的人為主人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了甚麼事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼事也不知道唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人，你真的甚麼也沒做過?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有做過甚麼特別的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常重要的事情，你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你告訴我，你做過甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人   仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.04,0:09:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以...欺負主人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和久留美...   接吻了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於已經長大成人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥我既高興又感到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊，我不是有意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是...巧合...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧合?你巧合地吻了她後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她便甦醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是沒可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要太過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的用愛的力量令久留美甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事只有我倆才明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的二人世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實...並非如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的主人就只有主人你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之事實就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳雖然那樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...   青空之下的青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士和我一起開發的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使二號機，沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是， ...這個地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些是鋼鐵天使的心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經確定後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右面的應該是沙希的中臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而另一個我就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有更大胸脯的鋼鐵天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以開動它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力一試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我的主人只有一個唷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的敵人正步步進迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?是誰?   不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是一個皮膚晰白的美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥...哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第三話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「新的天使，沙希」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容錯過...唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派報紙的人嗎?   不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派牛奶的嗎?   不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送豆腐的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，是...更加可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她是一個皮膚晰白美女
